window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Debt-serf. Scavenger. Nobody worth remembering.</b></p> <p>In Alnda, that’s all Alaric was ever supposed to be. Something others had planned for him.</p> <p>But with CD, Elli, Seo Rin, and Yesabel at his side, Alaric’s building mechs, making allies, and carving a future society never wanted him to have.</p> <p>Yet the world isn’t done trying to break him. Raiders strike the city. Gangster lords demand the impossible. And Boyerman tempts him with freedom for a hellish price.</p> <p>Alaric goes all in, ready to gamble not only just his own future, but that of everyone he cares about and loves for a chance to be free.</p> <p>Because in a land where power decides who stands and who kneels, he’s done living on his knees.</p>"; 
